{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-949ed9b337294e5a", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# AudioMosaic: Contrastive Masked Audio Representation Learning\narXiv: 2605.14231\nAuthors: Hanxun Huang, Qizhou Wang, Xingjun Ma, Cihang Xie, Christopher Leckie, Sarah Erfani\nYear: 2026 | Venue: \nTopic: \nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. AudioMosaic introduces a contrastive audio pre-training framework that uses structured time-frequency masking to construct complementary positive pairs for effective and efficient spectrogram-based learning.\n  2. A representation-level analysis using effective rank demonstrates that structured time-frequency masking prevents dimension collapse by reducing shared local redundancy between positive pairs.\n  3. AudioMosaic achieves state-of-the-art performance on multiple audio benchmarks, supports memory-efficient large-batch pre-training, and improves audio-language models when integrated as an audio encoder.\n\nTags: SSL, SSL/对比式", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "978ba9bf-23e0-4dc1-86a9-0fe72e55523f", "uuid": "8448e59a-4403-4d19-ba91-0656b8f0350b", "timestamp": "2026-07-12T11:24:53.444Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# AudioMosaic: Contrastive Masked Audio Representation Learning\narXiv: 2605.14231\nAuthors: Hanxun Huang, Qizhou Wang, Xingjun Ma, Cihang Xie, Christopher Leckie, Sarah Erfani\nYear: 2026 | Venue: \nTopic: \nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. AudioMosaic introduces a contrastive audio pre-training framework that uses structured time-frequency masking to construct complementary positive pairs for effective and efficient spectrogram-based learning.\n  2. A representation-level analysis using effective rank demonstrates that structured time-frequency masking prevents dimension collapse by reducing shared local redundancy between positive pairs.\n  3. AudioMosaic achieves state-of-the-art performance on multiple audio benchmarks, supports memory-efficient large-batch pre-training, and improves audio-language models when integrated as an audio encoder.\n\nTags: SSL, SSL/对比式", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
